RNA病毒本身，可能會對新冠病毒有效，該藥於2014年進入市場，最初是用於治療H5N1禽流感。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"疑住蘇聯啲嘢好勁副作用"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"佢的設計係單程咁，等如啲飛機飛到就得，降落唔需要諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"手術成功 但病人死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e8e81ec77cbfad985464c18a4088ce016650a2","tid":1865622,"uid":18741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"申請定專利未?"},{"pid":"70643eb6e626cd0f6d78835903655dba44d2e970","tid":1865622,"uid":129378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"蛆國強大，不靠外國貨"},{"pid":"1f6b35876348726836457b443f70541fabd146cb","tid":1865622,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"突然間偏方大發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2183f5c891adcc10cc6e75438d1f446acaa9e3f5","tid":1865622,"uid":331251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16f70af0e53fb69aa4d0d9c7ae2da76162517837","tid":1865622,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:41:13.000Z","msg":"就黎每日一篇"},{"pid":"f0256c04e724ac878b763f9c0b0771d845f6c6b4","tid":1865622,"uid":73192,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"玩夠fake news 未？<br />\n<br />\n講夠廢話未？ 造謠生事，警方執法未？"},{"pid":"48f4bf88113f9e14c7319740440cb02a3d2537ed","tid":1865622,"uid":220853,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"比中國發現左新招 <br />\n有新藥 = 有牛市<br />\n熊軍又輸<br />\n只要日日都有新藥  恆指可以升破十萬"},{"pid":"3af7a39f18cb3b72314b655f599d6437d19038e4","tid":1865622,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"毒藥？"},{"pid":"940783c726930bb6711182d03b2