送往中國，目前正測試該藥物對新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎的治療效果。大學一教授表示，三氮唑核苷治療的不是症狀，而是RNA病毒本身，可能會對新冠病毒有效，該藥於2014年進入市場，最初是用於治療H5N1禽流感。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"疑住蘇聯啲嘢好勁副作用"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"佢的設計係單程咁，等如啲飛機飛到就得，降落唔需要諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"單程潛艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8363b1b279980397be10f2b954f8a73c28df6659","tid":1865622,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"嘩, 日日都有藥話有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601e99642a8dbfefad03bc4e115b6722efaf9896","tid":1865622,"uid":187753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c78630ca3d904836363b26bb3ec30fa13b47dff","tid":1865622,"uid":28397,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"7500a75ce9a7fa6d0c89e30079a8c168a8bf8d40","tid":1865622,"uid":197640,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"8f6e7aa645c7ea01a90ae7cb73c8718a4272ec20","tid":1865622,"uid":28397,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"疑住蘇聯啲嘢好勁副作用"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"佢的設計係單程咁，等如啲飛機飛到就得，降落唔需要諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"手術成功 但病人死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依句真係好正"},{"pid":"88d000eb870ffe56d5b22f2b1054448594dc760b","tid":1865622,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T10:46:44.000Z","msg":"究竟中國肺炎解藥出先定流浮山200刀手出先"},{"pid":"35a081ec99645084ee4568cdab2f63cfdbf07716","tid":1865622,"uid":77318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af7a39f18cb3b72314b655f599d6437d19038e4","tid":1865622,"ui